  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d0e1f2a3b4c5d6, type: 3}
  m_Name: Roudra_Lore
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::GV.UI.CharacterLoreData
  characterName: Roudra
  tagline: Even the Devas must answer for injustice.
  rarity: Legendary
  role: Heavy Burst
  regionLabel: Kingdom
  regionName: Daitya Giri
  factionLabel: Faction
  factionName: Asuras
  powerClass: Supreme Astra Powers
  terrainMastery: Dual Terrain Mastery
  tharaResonance: Normal Thara Resonance
  backstory: "Once the most trusted general serving Nandana's Deva throne, Roudra
    served Aaryaveer's father for twenty years before discovering the truth:
    Nandana's golden supremacy was built on Daitya Giri's suffering. The
    Asura forges fed the Deva empire, Asura miners died in the volcanic depths, and
    the Deva king called it divine order. Roudra didn't betray Nandana -
    he liberated Daitya Giri. He wears the Om symbol on his chest plate as a reminder
    that divine authority means nothing without justice. Now he commands the volcanic
    forges, building the most devastating Astra weapons the Akasa Raajyas have ever
    seen."
  strengths: "Highest burst damage in the entire roster - Supreme Astra channeled
    through Asura forge-weapons\nArmor forged from Daitya Giri volcanic ore; nearly
    indestructible head-on\nDecades of battlefield experience - reads formations,
    not individuals"
  weaknesses: "Slowest pilot in the Trials; his weapons platform sacrifices all agility
    for firepower\nNormal Thara Resonance - devastating but unsustainable in
    prolonged fights\nOld injuries from the Forge Wars slow his reflexes"
  rivals: "Aaryaveer - The prince wants vengeance for his father\nZorvan -
    NEO-TERRAn who deserted his ranks\nVyanika - Garudaja raiders threatening
    his supply lines"
